To use ollama, add in the `__main__.py`  the secrets:

#-p OLLAMA_HOST "$OLLAMA_HOST" 
#-p AUTH "$AUTH" 

Never add code directly to `__main__.py`, just the metadata, provide the implemention code in the invoked function.

Assume the values of the metadata are availabie in the args and in the env (for test) and retrieve the secrets with

<SECRET> = args.get("<SECRET>", os.getenv("<SECRET>")

In the invoked function assess to Ollama building an URL  f"https://{auth}@{ollama_host}"
